                                 Howard 101
                             Jackie's Joke Hunt
                             November 10, 2009
                                           
		            128K COMMERCIAL FREE

      Special Guest:  Pat Cooper !!!
               
    * Jackie The Joke Man Martling Hosts An Hour Of All The Jokes & Gags
      You've Known Since His Role On The Howard Stern Show.  He May Have
      Left The Show But He Hasn't Left Radio.  Spark One Up And Listen.

      I'm so glad I started ripping this show!  The special guest tonight
      is Pat Cooper!!!  It's classic Cooper material that some of you old
      fans will find familiar and you new comers will learn to love.  This
      is another guest that seems to stray away from the Stern show along
      with Billy West.  Two great comedians that seem to have beef with
      Howard but not Jackie.  F Jackie!!!
